{"doc":{"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"color","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Reference\">CSS Reference</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Color\">CSS Color</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon non-standard\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"img\">\n    <title>This API has not been standardized.</title>\n    <path d=\"M50 92.5H6.09a4.47 4.47 0 01-3.87-6.71l22-38 22-38a4.46 4.46 0 017.74 0l22 38 22 38a4.47 4.47 0 01-3.87 6.71z\"></path>\n    <path d=\"M57.41 78.1A7.41 7.41 0 1150 70.7a7.39 7.39 0 017.41 7.4zm-2.14-14.89H44.81l-1.72-36h13.82z\" fill=\"#fff\"></path>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color-adjust\"><code>color-adjust</code></a></li><li><em><code>color</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/forced-color-adjust\"><code>forced-color-adjust</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/opacity\"><code>opacity</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\">The <strong><code>color</code></strong> CSS property sets the foreground <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\">color value</a> of an element's text and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/text-decoration\">text decorations</a>, and sets the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#currentcolor_keyword\"><code>&lt;currentcolor&gt;</code></a> value.</span> <code>currentcolor</code> may be used as an indirect value on <em>other</em> properties and is the default for other color properties, such as <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-color\"><code>border-color</code></a>.</p>\n\n<div><iframe class=\"interactive\" width=\"100%\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/css/color.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n\n<p class=\"hidden\">The source for this interactive example is stored in a GitHub repository. If you'd like to contribute to the interactive examples project, please clone <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples</a> and send us a pull request.</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>For an overview of using color in HTML, see <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Applying_color\">Applying color to HTML elements using CSS</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"brush: css no-line-numbers notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* Keyword values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> currentcolor<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;named-color&gt; values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> orange<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> tan<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> rebeccapurple<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;hex-color&gt; values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #090<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #009900<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #090a<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #009900aa<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;rgb()&gt; values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>34<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 12<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 64<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0.6<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>34<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 12<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 64<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0.6<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>34 12 64 / 0.6<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>34 12 64 / 0.3<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>34.0 12 64 / 60%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>34.6 12 64 / 30%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;hsl()&gt; values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">hsl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>30<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0.6<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">hsla</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>30<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0.6<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">hsl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>30 100% 50% / 0.6<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">hsla</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>30 100% 50% / 0.6<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">hsl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>30.0 100% 50% / 60%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">hsla</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>30.2 100% 50% / 60%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Global values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inherit<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> initial<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> unset<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>The <code>color</code> property is specified as a single <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\"><code>&lt;color&gt;</code></a> value.</p>\n\n<p>Note that the value must be a uniform <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color\"><code>color</code></a>. It can't be a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/gradient\"><code>&lt;gradient&gt;</code></a>, which is actually a type of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Values","title":"Values","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\"><code>&lt;color&gt;</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Sets the color of the textual and decorative parts of the element.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Accessibility_concerns","title":"Accessibility concerns","isH3":false,"content":"<p>It is important to ensure that the contrast ratio between the color of the text and the background the text is placed over is high enough that people experiencing low vision conditions will be able to read the content of the page.</p>\n\n<p>Color contrast ratio is determined by comparing the luminosity of the text and background color values. In order to meet current <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/WAI/intro/wcag\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG)</a>, a ratio of 4.5:1 is required for text content and 3:1 for larger text such as headings. Large text is defined as 18.66px and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/font-weight\">bold</a> or larger, or 24px or larger.</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://webaim.org/resources/contrastchecker/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebAIM: Color Contrast Checker</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/Understanding_WCAG/Perceivable#guideline_1.4_make_it_easier_for_users_to_see_and_hear_content_including_separating_foreground_from_background\">MDN Understanding WCAG, Guideline 1.4 explanations</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/UNDERSTANDING-WCAG20/visual-audio-contrast-contrast.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Understanding Success Criterion 1.4.3 | W3C Understanding WCAG 2.0</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Formal_definition","title":"Formal definition","isH3":false,"content":"<p><table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\">Initial value</a></th><td>Varies from one browser to another</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Applies to</th><td>all elements. It also applies to <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/::first-letter\"><code>::first-letter</code></a> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/::first-line\"><code>::first-line</code></a>.</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance\">Inherited</a></th><td>yes</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/computed_value\">Computed value</a></th><td>If the value is translucent, the computed value will be the <code>rgba()</code> corresponding one. If it isn't, it will be the <code>rgb()</code> corresponding one. The <code>transparent</code> keyword maps to <code>rgba(0,0,0,0)</code>.</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Animation type</th><td>a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#interpolation\" title=\"Values of the <color> CSS data type are interpolated on each of their red, green, blue components, each handled as a real, floating-point number. Note that interpolation of colors happens in the alpha-premultiplied sRGBA color space to prevent unexpected grey colors to appear.\">color</a></td></tr></tbody></table></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Formal_syntax","title":"Formal syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\" title=\"\">&lt;color&gt;</a><p style=\"font-family:Open Sans,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 10px 0 0 0;\">where <br><code style=\"font-family:Consolas,Monaco,&quot;Andale Mono&quot;,monospace;\"><span id=\"color\">&lt;color&gt;</span> = <a href=\"#rgb()\">&lt;rgb()&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> <a href=\"#rgba()\">&lt;rgba()&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> <a href=\"#hsl()\">&lt;hsl()&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> <a href=\"#hsla()\">&lt;hsla()&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> &lt;hex-color&gt; <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\">&lt;named-color&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> currentcolor <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\">&lt;deprecated-system-color&gt;</a></code></p><p style=\"font-family:Open Sans,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 10px 0 0 0;\">where <br><code style=\"font-family:Consolas,Monaco,&quot;Andale Mono&quot;,monospace;\"><span id=\"rgb()\">&lt;rgb()&gt;</span> = rgb( <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">{</a>3<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">}</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">[</a> / <a href=\"#alpha-value\">&lt;alpha-value&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">]</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark_()\" title=\"Question mark: the entity is optional\">?</a> ) <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> rgb( <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/number\" title=\"\">&lt;number&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">{</a>3<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">}</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">[</a> / <a href=\"#alpha-value\">&lt;alpha-value&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">]</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark_()\" title=\"Question mark: the entity is optional\">?</a> ) <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> rgb( <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#hash_mark_()\" title=\"Hash mark: the entity is repeated one or several times, each occurence separated by a comma\">#</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">{</a>3<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">}</a> , <a href=\"#alpha-value\">&lt;alpha-value&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark_()\" title=\"Question mark: the entity is optional\">?</a> ) <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> rgb( <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/number\" title=\"\">&lt;number&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#hash_mark_()\" title=\"Hash mark: the entity is repeated one or several times, each occurence separated by a comma\">#</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">{</a>3<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">}</a> , <a href=\"#alpha-value\">&lt;alpha-value&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark_()\" title=\"Question mark: the entity is optional\">?</a> )<br><span id=\"rgba()\">&lt;rgba()&gt;</span> = rgba( <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">{</a>3<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">}</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">[</a> / <a href=\"#alpha-value\">&lt;alpha-value&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">]</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark_()\" title=\"Question mark: the entity is optional\">?</a> ) <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> rgba( <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/number\" title=\"\">&lt;number&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">{</a>3<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">}</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">[</a> / <a href=\"#alpha-value\">&lt;alpha-value&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">]</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark_()\" title=\"Question mark: the entity is optional\">?</a> ) <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> rgba( <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#hash_mark_()\" title=\"Hash mark: the entity is repeated one or several times, each occurence separated by a comma\">#</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">{</a>3<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">}</a> , <a href=\"#alpha-value\">&lt;alpha-value&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark_()\" title=\"Question mark: the entity is optional\">?</a> ) <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> rgba( <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/number\" title=\"\">&lt;number&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#hash_mark_()\" title=\"Hash mark: the entity is repeated one or several times, each occurence separated by a comma\">#</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">{</a>3<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces_(_)\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">}</a> , <a href=\"#alpha-value\">&lt;alpha-value&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark_()\" title=\"Question mark: the entity is optional\">?</a> )<br><span id=\"hsl()\">&lt;hsl()&gt;</span> = hsl( <a href=\"#hue\">&lt;hue&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">[</a> / <a href=\"#alpha-value\">&lt;alpha-value&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">]</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark_()\" title=\"Question mark: the entity is optional\">?</a> ) <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> hsl( <a href=\"#hue\">&lt;hue&gt;</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a>, <a href=\"#alpha-value\">&lt;alpha-value&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark_()\" title=\"Question mark: the entity is optional\">?</a> )<br><span id=\"hsla()\">&lt;hsla()&gt;</span> = hsla( <a href=\"#hue\">&lt;hue&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">[</a> / <a href=\"#alpha-value\">&lt;alpha-value&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">]</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark_()\" title=\"Question mark: the entity is optional\">?</a> ) <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> hsla( <a href=\"#hue\">&lt;hue&gt;</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a>, <a href=\"#alpha-value\">&lt;alpha-value&gt;</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark_()\" title=\"Question mark: the entity is optional\">?</a> )</code></p><p style=\"font-family:Open Sans,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 10px 0 0 0;\">where <br><code style=\"font-family:Consolas,Monaco,&quot;Andale Mono&quot;,monospace;\"><span id=\"alpha-value\">&lt;alpha-value&gt;</span> = <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/number\" title=\"\">&lt;number&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a><br><span id=\"hue\">&lt;hue&gt;</span> = <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/number\" title=\"\">&lt;number&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/angle\" title=\"Possible values: a number followed by'deg', 'grad', 'rad' or 'turn', like 2turn, 1.3rad, -60deg or 0grad.\">&lt;angle&gt;</a></code></p></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Making_text_red","title":"Making text red","isH3":true,"content":"<p>The following are all ways to make a paragraph's text red:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #f00<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #ff0000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>255<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">hsl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 50% translucent */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #ff000080<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>255<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0.5<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">hsla</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0.5<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color/#the-color-property\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Color Module Level&nbsp;4<br><small lang=\"en-US\">The definition of 'color' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>Adds commaless syntaxes for the <code>rgb()</code>, <code>rgba()</code>, <code>hsl()</code>, and <code>hsla()</code> functions. Allows alpha values in <code>rgb()</code> and <code>hsl()</code>, turning <code>rgba()</code> and <code>hsla()</code> into (deprecated) aliases for them.<br>\n    Adds color keyword <code>rebeccapurple</code>.<br>\n    Adds 4- and 8-digit hex color values, where the last digit(s) represents the alpha value.<br>\n    Adds <code>hwb()</code>, <code>device-cmyk()</code>, and <code>color()</code> functions.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-3/#color\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Color Module Level&nbsp;3<br><small lang=\"en-US\">The definition of 'color' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Deprecates system-colors. Adds SVG colors. Adds the <code>rgba()</code>, <code>hsl()</code>, and <code>hsla()</code> functions.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/CSS2/colors.html#colors\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Level&nbsp;2 (Revision&nbsp;1)<br><small lang=\"en-US\">The definition of 'color' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Adds the <code>orange</code> color and the system colors.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/CSS1/#color\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Level&nbsp;1<br><small lang=\"en-US\">The definition of 'color' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"Browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"css.properties.color","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"See_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\"><code>&lt;color&gt;</code></a> data type</li>\n <li>Other color-related properties: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/background-color\"><code>background-color</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-color\"><code>border-color</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/outline-color\"><code>outline-color</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/text-decoration-color\"><code>text-decoration-color</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/text-emphasis-color\"><code>text-emphasis-color</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/text-shadow\"><code>text-shadow</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/caret-color\"><code>caret-color</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-rule-color\"><code>column-rule-color</code></a>, and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color-adjust\"><code>color-adjust</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Applying_color\">Applying color to HTML elements using CSS</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"Syntax"},{"text":"Accessibility concerns","id":"Accessibility_concerns"},{"text":"Formal definition","id":"Formal_definition"},{"text":"Formal syntax","id":"Formal_syntax"},{"text":"Examples","id":"Examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"Specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"Browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"See_also"}],"summary":"The color CSS property sets the foreground color value of an element's text and text decorations, and sets the <currentcolor> value.","popularity":0.0558,"modified":"2021-03-15T17:55:56.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"color","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"color","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"color","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"color","locale":"it","native":"Italiano"},{"title":"color","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"color","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"color","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Propriedade color do CSS","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"color","locale":"pt-PT","native":"Português (Europeu)"},{"title":"color","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/css/color","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/css/color/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/f4fb4c2d90a134366c280eec6cb599825981ad5d"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS: Cascading Style Sheets"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color","title":"color"}],"pageTitle":"color - CSS: Cascading Style Sheets | MDN","noIndexing":false}}